--- .gitignore (原始)
```
# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Editor/IDE files
.vscode/

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Logs
*.log

# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
*.js.map

# Python artifacts (if any Python files are added later)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
*.coverage

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.swp
*.swo

# Package managers
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# OS generated files
ehthumbs.db
Icon?
```

+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```
# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Editors
.vscode/

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*
```